{"name":"Arcane Reservoir","type":"feat","flags":{"importid":"vDhwFSnxFzZPYByp"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"HJIOotBk6VAZ9vT1","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Beginning of 2nd level, a scholar has an innate pool of magical energy that she can draw upon to fuel her scholar exploits and enhance her spells. The scholar&rsquo;s arcane reservoir can hold a maximum amount of magical energy equal to 3 + the scholar&rsquo;s level. Each day, after resting 8 hours, the scholar&rsquo;s arcane reservoir fills with raw magical energy, gaining a number of points equal to 3 + half of her scholar&rsquo;s level. She can also regain these points through the consume MP class feature and some scholar exploits. The arcane reservoir can never hold more points than the maximum amount noted above; points gained in excess of this total are lost.</p>\n<p>Points from the scholar reservoir are used to fuel many of the scholar&rsquo;s powers. In addition, the scholar can expend 1 point from her arcane reservoir as a free action whenever she casts a spell. If she does, she can choose to increase the caster level by 1 or increase the spell&rsquo;s DC by 1. She can expend no more than 1 point from her reservoir on a given spell in this way.</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","max":0,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"arcaneReservoir","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":["Scholar"]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"targe