{"name":"Scholar Exploit: Illusion Catcher","type":"feat","flags":{"importid":"Asu81l0zZBCP1YtV"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"Ojygv7pmN4ZwxF76","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Prerequisite(s):</strong> Face Thief scholar exploit<br /><br />The scholar gains a +2 bonus on saving throws against illusions. If the scholar successfully disbelieves an illusion, she can expend 1 point from her arcane reservoir to try to negate or steal control of the illusion. The scholar attempts a caster level check as if she were dispelling the effect with dispel. If she succeeds, she can either end the effect or alter it as if she were the spell&rsquo;s caster. If the spell&rsquo;s duration is concentration, the scholar must concentrate on the new effect or it ends.</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":["Scholar Exploit"],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","max":0,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[{"text":"+2 bonus on saving throws against illusions. If the scholar successfully disbelieves an illusion, she can expend 1 point from her arcane reservoir to try to negate or steal control of the illusion. The scholar attempts a caster level check as if she were dispelling the effect with dispel. If she succeeds, she can either end the effect or alter it as if she were the spell’s caster. If the spell’s duration is concentration, the scholar must concentrate on the new effect or it ends.","target":"savingThrows","subTarget":"allSavingThrows"}],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"illusionCatcher","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":["Scholar"]},"showInQuickbar":false,"ability